&lt;li&gt;Deep understanding of tuning techniques (SFT, DPO, RL) and the underlying mathematical principles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of infrastructural components that enterprises commonly use, such as databricks, S3/GCS storage, SageMaker, artifact registry etc&lt;/li&gt;
