&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ensuring System Reliability:&lt;/strong&gt; Ensure systems are designed and implemented with high availability, scalability, and performance. Focus on fault tolerance, disaster recovery, identifying and removing scaling bottlenecks, and performance optimization across our multi-cloud infrastructure.&lt;/li&gt;
