&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Capacity Planning &amp;amp; Performance Tuning:&lt;/strong&gt; Work proactively on capacity planning to ensure our infrastructure can gracefully handle growth and peak loads. Optimize system performance and resource utilization.&lt;/li&gt;
