&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hands-on experience with LLM evaluations and/or post-training methods&lt;/strong&gt;: How to design useful evals and use their results to guide model improvement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Engineering Skills: &lt;/strong&gt;The ability to work across backend systems and developer-facing product surfaces. Comfortable shipping full-stack features when needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Understanding of the GenAI Lifecycle:&lt;/strong&gt; You understand the end-to-end workflow—from prompting a base model to curating a dataset, fine-tuning, and productionizing agents—and how these steps interconnect.&lt;/li&gt;
